## 1. Purpose

This document is the first required read for any developer or AI coding agent working on the Musahama platform.

It explains:
- what the platform is
- how the system is structured
- what the official vocabulary is
- what the most common implementation mistakes are
- what must be read before making changes

---

## 2. What This Platform Is

This is an AI-assisted research and discovery platform for organizations.

The business workflow is:

CRM Opportunity
→ Mandate
→ Research Run
→ Strategy Generation
→ Results
→ Evidence / Analysis
→ Fit Scoring
→ Dossier / Output
→ CRM Sync / Export

The platform is:
- organization-centric
- multi-tenant
- module-driven
- feature-gated
- source-of-truth disciplined

